<Author>ExplorerGR
<Content>Bad Service/Bad Food I stayed in this hotel 8 nights (I wish I could move to another hotel but it had been already paid by my company). Everyday I was negotiating with the lady answering the phone from the room sevice, to bring me a coffee in my room. One time she told me that i should come downstairs to pick it up instead of calling the room sevice as the hotel was very busy...It is the first time in my life that I stay in a NOVOTEL and I face such problems..and the problem was repeated every day.... The food was unacceptable, and generally i think that the NOVOTEL standards are not followed in this hotel. 
